resources.string: Group Maker is a generator that creates random teams or groups. Through this application can help you to divide the list of names into a team or group. By entering a list of names into the team generator, the team generator will randomize the names you entered earlier. You can also set the number of groups or the number of people in a group that you want to create to produce a randomly evenly distributed group within a group
